# goal-flight

- Treat repository Markdown plus Git as canonical state.
- Load `AGENTS.md` when present, then `SKILL.md` or generated host wrapper
  instructions for Goal Flight commands.
- On Goal Flight init, verify `gstack` is available before using gstack review
  commands. If missing, surface a setup action instead of silently continuing.
- Do not auto-approve broad shell, network, auth, update, package-registry, or
  model-consuming probes.
- Keep machine-local readiness in state files, not checked-in adapter manifests.
